WEBVTT

00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:02.080
filling buckets with water from a tap.

00:01:03.360 --> 00:01:05.336
I even saw children,

00:01:05.360 --> 00:01:08.016
who looked the same age as me,

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:10.416
filling up these clear plastic bottles

00:01:10.440 --> 00:01:13.520
with dirty water
from streams on the roadside.

00:01:14.880 --> 00:01:16.576
Watching these kids

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.736
forced to drink water

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:21.776
that I felt was too dirty to touch

00:01:21.800 --> 00:01:23.960
changed my perspective on the world.

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:28.576
This unacceptable social injustice

00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:31.656
compelled me to want to find a solution